{"tid":345810,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[天朝集團] 尼馬轉會觸焦","createTime":"2017-08-03T11:38:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-03T12:03:53.000Z","uid":54373,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4470f85b04123a0aa87e53141616720ce81d8c17","tid":345810,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T11:38:40.000Z","msg":"多間西班牙傳媒周四報道，西甲賽會拒絕收下巴塞隆拿前鋒尼馬所交的違約金。<br />\n<br />\n尼馬的律師Juan de Dios Crespo周四到西甲聯賽會的辦公室，繳交2.2億歐元（約20億港元）的違約金。然而，西甲聯賽並不接受，令這宗天價轉會再生波折。尼馬方面計劃周五向國際足協轉會部門申請，為巴黎聖日耳門（PSG）出戰，希望本周內解決轉會問題。<br />\n<br />\n西甲聯賽會主席泰巴斯早前說過，他們會向歐洲足協舉報PSG違反財政公平條例，所以他絕不會接受這份違約金。然而，西班牙《馬卡報》稱，若果尼馬能夠支付違約金，西甲聯賽不能限制他轉會。至於PSG是否違反財政公平條例，那就是轉會落實後的事。"},{"pid":"3ed5632c39c5ee30766b57130aa32f63e558d172","tid":345810,"uid":48631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T11:46:08.000Z","msg":"玩大D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fcffed8f7746c4b20b0cfe9e4892d3d5fff78cf","tid":345810,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T11:46:45.000Z","msg":"go mu la diu"},{"pid":"214caa78e0866ff6bfdafb6296db7fc710c952fe","tid":345810,"uid":8951,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T11:48:30.000Z","msg":"你唔收佢又點違反呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce404cde276a15286c572525a7b7d22950170d75","tid":345810,"uid":46151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T11:48:45.000Z","msg":"又話俾300m買肖像權 然後自由轉會？"},{"pid":"c0221925375e6323759c9c532ec3ad29f39524d6","tid":345810,"uid":34468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T12:01:26.000Z","msg":"人地違反關你撚事咩咁關心人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d49deae78f0ef7c9823519109a244d1fea656a81","tid":345810,"uid":4826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T12:03:14.000Z","msg":"鳩踢囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f3fd